msg_1:
[color(yellow)]Sakya[color(white)]
[tab]I am Sakya... One awakened from "Maya". 
[tab]If the reality is an illusion bound by Jiva... 
[wait][clear][color(yellow)]Sakya[color(white)]
[tab]Let us preach enlightenment together so as to 
[tab]release living beings from their spiritual bondage.
[wait][clear][end]

